name: Book of Core Beliefs
description: A large, heavy book lying open on a lectern. Its pages describe a fundamental belief, such as "I must be perfect to be worthy."

name: Pot of Nourishing Soup

name: Tapestry of a Past Success
description: A tapestry depicting a time you successfully navigated a difficult social situation. The colors are vibrant and clear.
